      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Ayo, you''re not from here you. Welcome to Narda !

    I''m Bioup. Who
    are you ? You don''t remember ?

    You lost what ? Your eyes !? And one of
    them keeps your memory ?

    Are you embarking on a self-search? Good luck my
    friend'
